    "AI-driven monitoring enables decision-makers to dynamically adjust strategies, ensuring more effective disaster response efforts (Nakhaei et al., 2023).",
    "AI strengthens disaster management across all phasesprevention, preparedness, response, and recovery (Nakhaei et al., 2023; Sun L. et al., 2024).",
    "AI-driven decision support systems optimize resource allocation, enhance early warning systems, and facilitate rapid damage assessment, enabling communities to recover more efficiently (Hossin et al., 2025).",
